        <title>Workspace Content</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>If you have archived your draft, that would be in a workspace, but not in the inbox. Likewise you could flag a draft, and set your inbox for the workspace not to include flagged drafts.</p>
<p>I wrote a post a few years back where I tried to explain the details of the  differences between the folders. Maybe that will help too?</p>
